I forgot how much talking to you made me feel better.
Why am I sad over some idiot with no personality again?

I hate you for making me feel this way.
I want so desperately to be better. I'll do anything.
hearts will never be practical until they can be made unbreakable

You could be happy and I won't know
But you weren't happy the day I watched you go

And all the things that I wished I had not said
Are played in loops 'till it's madness in my head

Is it too late to remind you how we were
But not our last days of silence, screaming, blur

Most of what I remember makes me sure
I should have stopped you from walking out the door

You could be happy, I hope you are
You made me happier than I'd been by far

Somehow everything I own smells of you
And for the tiniest moment it's all not true

Do the things that you always wanted to
Without me there to hold you back, don't think, just do

More than anything I want to see you, girl
Take a glorious bite out of the whole world
sometimes good things fall apart so better things can fall together

"You closed your eyes. That was the difference. Sometimes you cannot believe what you see, you have to believe what you feel. And if you are ever going to have other people trust you, you must feel that you can trust them too-even when you are in the dark. Even when you're falling."

seriously, fuck everybody. I'm so sick of 90% of the people who are in my life.


I was not put on this earth as means of transportation for people
-Just because you hang out with me for 10 minuites does not mean I'm obligated to drive you home in bfe so you can go to work. (I drove slow on purpose btw) 
-If you haven't even spoken to me in months, don't all of the sudden text me and ask me for a ride. (and don't call me a bitch when I say no) 
-If I do give you a ride somewhere, don't make me wait outside/in your house for 15+ minuites while you do bullshit, I'm going to start leaving people, it's your problem if you're late, not mine.
I'm not an idiot, I know when I'm being used and if you've done it, you're a shitty friend. coughcough.

Q; mexican food, atrium cleaning, drunken family members, time change, weird shopping, war stories, arguing about politics, music 24/7, and tons of looove.

A; what is texas?

school tomorrow, and I'm a little dissapointed because of what didn't happen today, I was looking foward to new beginnings.
I wish I could just stay home and sleep and never get up at 5:30 in the morning to go to some place with people who I don't even care about and who I know don't care about me either, just to sit and stare at some teacher and not learn a thing. I don't know why I was in such a hurry to escape three oaks, I miss being around people who pay attention to me. I miss having a best friend too, having a non-corrupt, nice, caring best friend. Thinking about how things used to be makes me want to cry but I won't because I'm sick of breaking promises to myself and everybody else and I'm sick of crying more than anything in the world. I want so much for my life to change, but at the same time I want it to be the way it was again. I was so happy.
I'm going to go take nap #2 now.

I've been hearing about some of the things that have been happening with people lately, and it makes me think about a few months ago, when I was in almost that same situation.
I find it so weird that one person can attract so many people at one time. How do you do it? You're a disgusting man whore with swollen lips.
I don't know how it is that certain boys can make people so blind.
Lately I've been actually seeing the boy who made me miserable for months, and I find myself wanting to smack me for that. He was not worth it, not at all. Even though sometimes I still miss him. But Leilani was right all along and I am happier without.
I hope this other guy doesn't break peoples hearts.
